# {{ project_name }} — GitHub Copilot instructions

The authoritative process lives in `docs/process/`. If this repository has
just been initialized, start with `docs/process/start-here.md` and guide the
user through Greenfield or Brownfield as a dialogue. For normal work, also
read the product frame `PRODUCT.md` (the direction every change is checked
against), `docs/process/mandatory-rules.md`, `docs/process/risk-tiers.md`,
`docs/process/workflow.md` (the phases: Brainstorm, Plan, Execute, Review,
Quick, Debug), and `docs/process/commits.md` (branching, merge routes, plan
archiving). Task-scoped prompts for each phase live under `.github/prompts/`.

